Package: SIMpoly
Title: Simulation of genetic marker data of individuals in pedigreed populations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marcelo", "Mollinari", , "mmollin@ncsu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7001-8498"))
Description: This package simulates genetic marker data of individuals in pedigreed populations. It enables users to model multigenerational, fixed-ploidy populations and analyze allele distributions.
